{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Are you ready to learn a new language?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash your linguistic prowess with <strong>Speechbound</strong>, a <i>multi platform language learning RPG</i> where the thrill of gaming and the power of education converge!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/steamZero.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Zero</strong> is going to have to explore this strange new land, and learn the language of its people in order to help rebuild the moon\u2019s community, get them out from under the rule of the oppressive <strong>SunCorp\u2122</strong>, and save the galaxy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerCOMMUNICATE.png?t=1728671906\" />Recover stolen language and use it to talk to NPCs, discover secrets, engage in conversations, and immerse yourself a rich storyline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_comm.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerEXPLORE.png?t=1728671906\" />Venture out into the world of Babyl Moon Station! Travel different biomes, face danger, and unravel the mysteries of the alien infestation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_expl.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerINTERACT.png?t=1728671906\" />Scan objects in the world, solve puzzles, and build your understanding as you study a new language!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_inter.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerSAVETHEWORLD.png?t=1728671906\" />Battle an ominous alien threat, help rebuild the station, heal the environment, and restore peace to a diverse community of characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_battle.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerCOOK.png?t=1728671906\" />Gather ingredients and practice vocabulary as you craft delicious meals to help you survive the dangers of exploration!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_cook.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerGOTOSCHOOL.png?t=1728671906\" />Visit the school to sharpen your grammar skills, learn about sentence structures, specific rules and exceptions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/WEB_class.gif?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/extras/bannerLine.png?t=1728671906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in a captivating narrative, interact with diverse characters, battle formidable foes, tackle exciting language exercises, and discover the beautifully hand-crafted world of <i><strong>Babyl Moon</strong></i>. At <strong>Moonspire Games</strong>, our mission is to transform the way you learn languages - making it immersive, engaging, and above all, unforgettable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With your support we're planning on integrating the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>English, Chinese, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, French, Italian</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Add it to your wishlist! </strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2521500?t=1728671906","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521500/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1